<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>SchoolHub</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("partials/header", { school: typeof school !== "undefined" ? school : null }) %>
  <main class="home-container">
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <span class="hero-badge">School Community Platform</span>
        <h1>SchoolHub</h1>
        <p>
          학교를 선택하고 학생 커뮤니티에 입장하세요.
          공지, 게시판, 건의사항을 한곳에서 확인할 수 있습니다.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#school-list" class="primary-action">학교 선택하기</a>
          <a href="/support" class="secondary-action">문의센터</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-card">
        <div class="hero-card-top">
          <span></span>
          <span></span>
          <span></span>
        </div>

        <h2>오늘의 SchoolHub</h2>
        <p>학생들이 더 편하게 소통할 수 있는 학교 커뮤니티를 만들어가는 중입니다.</p>

        <div class="hero-mini-grid">
          <div>
            <strong>게시판</strong>
            <span>승인제 운영</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>공지</strong>
            <span>관리자 등록</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>건의</strong>
            <span>의견 접수</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="school-section" id="school-list">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">SELECT SCHOOL</span>
          <h2>학교 선택</h2>
          <p>검색해서 학교 커뮤니티를 찾아보세요.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="search-box">
          <input 
            type="text" 
            id="schoolSearch" 
            placeholder="학교 이름 검색"
            autocomplete="off"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="school-list">
        <% schools.forEach(school => { %>
          <a 
            class="school-card" 
            href="/schools/<%= school.slug %>"
            data-school-name="<%= school.name %>"
          >
            <div>
              <span class="school-badge">입장 가능</span>
              <h3><%= school.name %></h3>
              <p>커뮤니티 입장 →</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        <% }) %>
      </div>

      <div class="no-result" id="noResult">
        검색 결과가 없습니다.
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script>
    const searchInput = document.getElementById("schoolSearch");
    const schoolCards = document.querySelectorAll(".school-card");
    const noResult = document.getElementById("noResult");

    searchInput.addEventListener("input", () => {
      const keyword = searchInput.value.trim().toLowerCase();
      let visibleCount = 0;

      schoolCards.forEach(card => {
        const schoolName = card.dataset.schoolName.toLowerCase();

        if (schoolName.includes(keyword)) {
          card.style.display = "block";
          visibleCount++;
        } else {
          card.style.display = "none";
        }
      });

      noResult.style.display = visibleCount === 0 ? "block" : "none";
    });
  </script>
  <%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>